# screen //创建 screen 终端

# screen vi /home/file //创建 screen 终端 ，并执行 vi命令

离开 screen 终端:ctrl+d

# screen -ls  //显示已创建的screen终端 
There are screens on:
	17631.pts-0.localhost	(Detached)
	17598.pts-0.localhost	(Detached)
2 Sockets in /var/run/screen/S-root.

# screen -r 17631 //连接 screen_id 为 17631 的 screen终端
